  "a410600E4-B3D9-7DD0-452A-5BD58E6C1896": {
    "parent": "aE98DE268-A605-6B3A-06E7-578BABC25D61",
    "id": "22",
    "title": "VertiPaq Analyzer",
    "type": "text",
    "completed": false,
    "text": "<p>VertiPaq Analyzer is the ultimate tool when analyzing the structure of an Analysis Services Tabular or Power BI model. You want to watch this training to better grasp all the details and the vast amount of information that VertiPaq Analyzer provides. The goal of the video course is to explain in detail what the information returned by VertiPaq actually means, and to showcase how you can use it practically.</p>\r\n<p>The course is divided into sections. We suggest that you watch the entire course at least once, to get acquainted with the various pages and their content. Only then will you be able to use the individual videos as a reference to refresh your understanding of the usage of the information on each page. You may want to use our bookmarks to that effect.</p>\r\n<p>At the end of the training, you can find a practical analysis of a real data model; the analysis shows you how to leverage the information in VertiPaq Analyzer to better understand a data model.</p>\r\n<p>Download the latest version of VertiPaq Analyzer at <a href=\"https://www.sqlbi.com/tools/vertipaq-analyzer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.sqlbi.com/tools/vertipaq-analyzer/</a></p>\r\n<p>Below you can download the sample files used in the lectures.</p>",
    "video": "",
    "duration": 0,
    "nop": false,
    "files": [
